uk.ac.ebi.pride.utilities.data.exporters

Class AbstractMzTabConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ebi.pride.jmztab.utils.convert.ConvertProvider<DataAccessController,Void>
      • uk.ac.ebi.pride.utilities.data.exporters.AbstractMzTabConverter
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MzIdentMLMzTabConverter, PRIDEMzTabConverter

    public abstract class AbstractMzTabConverter
extends uk.ac.ebi.pride.jmztab.utils.convert.ConvertProvider<DataAccessController,Void>
    ms-data-core api will plan to export all the data to mztab files using the jmzTab library. At the very beginning we will support only the Identification exporter, but in the future we should be able to support Quantitation export.
    Author:
    ypriverol, rwang
